document_data.mainbody:
liah Coastoar was a seller in the Moonsea in the late 15 century DR.
Eliah worked at Doctor Jubals Carnival of Curiosities as a seller of wine and pies.
Circa 1486 DR, Eliah noticed that Jubal had brought four new attractions to the carnival Madame Darkness, a mirror maze, dancing rats, and some fools.
